<head>EXILE</head>
    <list type="altnames">
<item>BANISHMENT</item>
<item>EXPULSION</item>
<item>EXPATRIATION</item>
<item>DEPORTATION</item>
    </list>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">流亡</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>LEAVE the STATE or CAUSE TO LEAVE the STATE.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The standard word for voluntary exile is wáng 亡.</p>
<p>2. Chū 出 is a polite periphrastic term occasionally used for going into exile.</p>
        </div>
<div type="modern-chinese-criteria">
<p>流刑</p>
